/realtime/article/20190325/59408787\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190325%2F59408787&d=Fb7z1ilWoLc7MobAJ3fbq%2BBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=17fc0548\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190325%2F59408787&h=88dfeb6a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190325/59408787</a><br />\n<br />\n2013年至今錄得154宗麻疹個案，當中被界定為外地傳入的有66宗，最多是來自<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">支那</span></strong>、菲律賓和印尼，分別佔<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">34宗</span></strong>、17宗及6宗，另外8宗分別由日本、台灣、印度、巴基斯坦、美國、澳洲、意大利、肯尼亞，各傳入1宗；餘下1宗因有關病人周遊列國，未能界定傳入地區。"},{"pid":"132c5e9c7c354357b9bd1d06bd88f9e0baf80875","tid":1077830,"uid":22141,"like":169,"dislike":1,"score":168,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T03:55:55.000Z","msg":"正常香港出世同係香港讀小學既人都有打過疫苗<br />\n中招個d一係新香港人<br />\n一係就打過都中 但機率低好多<br />\n一針已經有93% 兩針有97%"},{"pid":"b15e4c4dfb9c0ecc64a46f8feb2217c00ff61049","tid":1077830,"uid":53466,"like":67,"dislike":1,"score":66,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T03:55:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eab980e2b4b0f1a1225004c4af3e03bfbd00a9a8","tid":1077830,"uid":79563,"like":63,"dislike":0,"score":63,"quote":{"pid":"b15e4c4dfb9c0ecc64a46f8feb2217c00ff61049","tid":1077830,"uid":53466,"like":67,"dislike":1,"score":66,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T03:55:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T03:57:12.000Z","msg":"同沙士時一樣囉<br />\n<br />\n根本陸路邊境就係爆發既源頭<br />\n<br />\n政治原因害死299條人命"},{"pid":"275ee27f7ceae0b0dee60446a17ddf3103eac3a4","tid":1077830,"uid":156363,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T03:57:59.000Z","msg":"除非變種唔係發下夢算啦"},{"pid":"d6bc3e0067cf920648d7e45c883bc3b16716df27","tid":1077830,"uid":58335,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"132c5e9c7c354357b9bd1d06bd88f9e0baf80875","tid":1077830,"uid":22141,"like":169,"dislike":1,"score":168,"citedBy":7,"replyTi